Writer: John O'Brien (screenplay), John O'Brien (story), Jonathan L. Davis (story), Gy Waldron (characters)
Title: The Dukes of Hazzard
Actors: Johnny Knoxville, Seann William Scott, Alice Greczyn, Steve Lemme
Plot: Cousins Bo, Luke, and Daisy Duke, and their uncle Jesse, egg on the authorities of Hazzard County, Boss Hogg and Sheriff Coltrane.
